column5: Got out for a few hours this morning and managed 3 lakers and herring. Jaydub with big fish of the day at 9.7 pounds.  Nice fish.  Mine went 7.8 and his second was 5.7 pounds. Nice morning out on the lake.  I haven't seen it so flat out there in a long time.
nice pictures & fish, looks like a good morning on the water!
Really nice fish there, sounds like a nice day
nice fish. I have never caught a lake trout.  Matt.

riggers.  I have them on my boat, I just hide them under the back seat. The best part is that I decided to run a Strike king KVD 2.5 square bill crankbait in sexy shad colour on one rod and it actually caught Jon's second laker. lol, i love those lures
So you can catch something other then bass and colds?  Nice fishes.  Thursday morning the bay was flat calm as wellâ€¦ I noticed on my way to work.
And to think I canceled yesterdays fish because of the weather:wallbash:Nice catch Chris!!!!
Whats with the bad calls on the weather  :wallbash:  Nice fish Chris
Wow Nice Fish Guys ! Strong Lakers ! Number #4 On The Bucket List (Lake Trout) I have Never Personally Landed One.....Hats Off too Ya's
Was an awesome morning!  Probably could have got 1 or 2 more if we weren't dragging a herring around for the last hour or so.  Lol
nice fish - great day to be on the water.
